In Premier League's Boxing Day, Theo Walcott hits a hat-trick as Arsenal beat Newcastle United 7–3 while Manchester City cling on for a thrilling 4–3 victory over Norwich City at Carrow Road. (ESPN) (BBC) (Eurosport)In road bicycle racing, Daniel Martin wins 2013 Liège–Bastogne–Liège ahead of Joaquim Rodríguez and Alejandro Valverde. (BBC) (Cycling News)